          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " plastic scintillators"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " two multiwire proportional chambers",
                " The neutrons were recorded by neutron detectors of",
                "three types. The low-energy neutron-spectrum section",
                "between 0.5 and 3 MeV was measured at an angle of 120-",
                "degree in experiments with beryllium and lead targets",
                "by means of detector D1 based on a thin stilbene",
                "crystal. The region of energies above 2 to 3 MeV was",
                "studied with the aid of detectors D2 based on stilbene",
                "crystals of a larger volume and detectors D3 based on a",
                "thick plastic scintillator. The distances from the",
                "target to the neutron detectors were 64 cm for D1,",
                "  115 to 125 cm for D2 and 200 to 220 cm for D3.",
                "Veto counters based on thin plastic scintillators",
                "and arranged in front of the neutron detectors were",
                "used to discriminate charged particles."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
