              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By author*.The total correction for the loss",
                "of neutrons because of interaction in the target,",
                "the veto-detector scintillators and the lead layer in",
                "front of the neutron detector and because of scattering",
                "into the detector as the neutrons traverse the target",
                "was 11%, on average. This was not so only for a number",
                "of measurements with Be, Al, and Cu targets, where this",
                "correction was as large as 27%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": 16.0,
                "maximum_value": 25.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".The systematic error associated",
                "with determining the number of target atoms and the",
                "number of protons that hit the target, as well as with",
                "taking into account the background, ranged from 16",
                "to 25% for various angles and detectors."
              ]
            }
          ],
